    {
      "id": 125099,
      "name": "Locus-Walker",
      "elite": false,
      "quotes": [
        {
          "soundId": 87824,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-15-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688860,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/28/1688860/VO_73_Locus-Walker_15_M.ogg",
          "text": "Disrupting their efforts would benefit us all. Also, their commander here has a particular item that would be useful to me.",
          "status": "accepted",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87829,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-20-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688865,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/33/1688865/VO_73_Locus-Walker_20_M.ogg",
          "text": "It is rare that a naaru falls into Void this way. The few cases I know of have occurred when mortals were involved. What fascinating implications...",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87836,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-27-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688872,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/40/1688872/VO_73_Locus-Walker_27_M.ogg",
          "text": "Let's not get ahead of ourselves. We need to test the limits of this newfound power. Come.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87830,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-21-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688866,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/34/1688866/VO_73_Locus-Walker_21_M.ogg",
          "text": "Such musings can wait, though. This entity must die.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87825,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-16-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688861,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/29/1688861/VO_73_Locus-Walker_16_M.ogg",
          "text": "Thank you for removing the obstacles between me and this staff, heroes.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87831,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-22-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688867,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/35/1688867/VO_73_Locus-Walker_22_M.ogg",
          "text": "The Void is a force of change... of transformation. Shadows are fluid, ever shifting.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87857,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-48-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688922,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/90/1688922/VO_73_Locus-Walker_48_M.ogg",
          "text": "Yes, the naaru. We must get inside. Alleria, the skills you have learned can open the way.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87835,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-26-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688871,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/39/1688871/VO_73_Locus-Walker_26_M.ogg",
          "text": "You asked me to teach you to use the Void as a weapon. Now that weapon is you.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87832,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-23-m",
          "fileDataId": 1688868,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/36/1688868/VO_73_Locus-Walker_23_M.ogg",
          "text": "You stand on the cusp of destiny, Alleria. There will be choices to make... and consequences to face.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 87834,
          "filename": "vo-73-locus-walker-25-m",
